text: Walter Martinez (born 26 March 1991) is a Honduran football player who plays for F.C. Motagua in the Liga Nacional de Fútbol Profesional de Honduras.https://us.soccerway.com/players/walter-martinez/282156/ On 28 May 2018 Martinez made his senior debut for the Honduras national football team against South Korea.https://us.soccerway.com/matches/2018/05/28/world/friendlies/korea- republic/honduras/2757157/ ==References== Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Honduran footballers Category:Liga Nacional de Fútbol Profesional de Honduras players Category:Honduran Liga Nacional de Ascenso players Category:C.D.
